  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/0a6e806e924bf011c6724d19e5d8cdb4.avif?t=1753273050\" width=600 height=116 /></span><br><br>\"Once Upon a Rogue's Tale” combines strategic roguelike deckbuilding with the luck of the dice. Roll the dice and trade them in battle to play your cards. Dice also allow you to unleash powerful character abilities to your advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/938571e33e0654a6cf7884e1328d03af.poster.avif?t=1753273050\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/938571e33e0654a6cf7884e1328d03af.webm?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/938571e33e0654a6cf7884e1328d03af.mp4?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Out of combat, you'll encounter events that will confront you with tough decisions. The choices you make will affect how the story unfolds, which will be written down in your personal storybook.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/584d52138398a5c60b85eca1c6cb7e15.poster.avif?t=1753273050\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/584d52138398a5c60b85eca1c6cb7e15.webm?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/584d52138398a5c60b85eca1c6cb7e15.mp4?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The fairytale worlds have mixed...</h2>Little Red Riding Hood, Jack and the Beanstalk and The Frog Prince find themselves in an adventurous tangle of fairytales. Choose one of the classic characters, make your own decisions and influence the course of the story. Team up with strong allies and collect magical items to help you on your way through the colorful fairytale world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/ac4410b4238f0c9769476a068b14d117.poster.avif?t=1753273050\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/ac4410b4238f0c9769476a068b14d117.webm?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/ac4410b4238f0c9769476a068b14d117.mp4?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategical deepness through positioning</h2>Positioning is especially important in battles with multiple opponents and adds strategic depth to the game. Use certain abilities to influence the position of your characters and apply special effects to your opponents to be able to attack them from anywhere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/ae5103923dd6f504ea4cc014f75f0c9e.poster.avif?t=1753273050\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/ae5103923dd6f504ea4cc014f75f0c9e.webm?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/ae5103923dd6f504ea4cc014f75f0c9e.mp4?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle between good and evil</h2>Each character has their own motivations that have led them to the good or evil side. But ultimately, the decision is yours: will former villains become new friends or will you turn the entire fairytale world against you? Your actions determine the fate of the fairytale characters and blur the lines between friend and foe.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/9fdef81469d674cce74134e7f1fb12e5.poster.avif?t=1753273050\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/9fdef81469d674cce74134e7f1fb12e5.webm?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/9fdef81469d674cce74134e7f1fb12e5.mp4?t=1753273050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602540/extras/40a4056f866a77593df8a7f3b58c87d2.avif?t=1753273050\" width=600 height=103 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Revisit your favourite fairytales in a wholesome anime inspired artstyle<br></li><li>Experience randomly generated runs with high replayability<br></li><li>Gather helpful allies and collect powerful items<br></li><li>Use cards and dice to defeat your opponents<br></li><li>Master the positioning mechanic to unlock a new level of strategy</li></ul>",
